        <title>Hunger</title>
        <description>&lt;img src=&quot;/img/autumn.jpg&quot; class=&quot;article-image right&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;article-quote&quot;&gt;
    “I&#39;ve started reading Hamsun&#39;s ‘Hunger’”, I interrupted.&lt;br&gt;
    “Oh, that&#39;s not something you want to read unless you&#39;re in a really good mood!” he exclaimed.&lt;br&gt;
    “I haven&#39;t read it”, she said.
    I downed the rest of the negroni. “Ylajali...”
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
    And that was pretty much it. The clouds had dispersed, revealing the sun, and I walked back home, slightly intoxicated.
&lt;/p&gt;
